146
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,900
Give me the key!

147
00:10:34,330 --> 00:10:35,440
Don't pay attention!

148
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:39,150
Since they look like humans
they do impressions of people!

149
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:42,870
