Count on me, Straw Hat!

176
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:15,420
Follow me...

177
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:30,270
Oh no. There's something
here. And what the...

178
00:12:30,270 --> 00:12:32,260
Ow, ow, ow, ow...

179
