210
00:14:48,490 --> 00:14:50,880
Miso flavored noodle!

211
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,950
Salt flavored noodle!

212
00:14:52,950 --> 00:14:55,180
Soy sauce flavored noodle!

213
